<p>Depending on the status, please review the relevant feedback below to determine your next steps:</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>Client Feedback:</strong> {{CLIENT_REMARKS}}</li>
	<li><strong>Manager Feedback:</strong> {{MANAGER_REMARKS}}</li>
</ul>

<hr />
<p><strong>Action Items:</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>If <strong>Approved</strong>: No further action is needed on the budget. Prepare for the next phase.</li>
	<li>If <strong>Changes Requested</strong>: Please log in to Salesforce, address the remarks, and re-submit the budget for approval.</li>
</ul>
